This is DoomFrequency, 


https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3697471948


  


The mod is currently tested and usable, and we have some WiP roadmap:

- Quest system: the NPC will assign tasks, and will improve Karma on execution. Good karma will result in rewards, such as materials, ammo, or weapons.

- Skill training: the NPC expertise can lead him to teach you certain skills, given enough Karma. For example, Silas Vance, a seasoned electrical engineer, could teach you how to operate generators.
